## ðŸŽ¯ Interview Tips
- Always identify the **base case**
- Draw the **recursion tree**
- Know **time & space complexity**
- Convert recursion to iteration if needed

---

## ðŸš€ Best Way to Learn Recursion
1. Trace with small inputs
2. Dry run on paper
3. Understand call stack
4. Practice problems daily

